2026-02-25 15:13:29,919 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': 'authorize.js:146-165 — replace both `hasReadOnlyPermission()` call and `findMenuNode()` call with: `const page = req.session.pages && req.session.pages[appId]; if (page && page.ronly) return blocked`.'}
2026-02-25 15:13:32,869 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': 'authorize.js — remove `findMenuNode()` (lines 80-94), remove `hasReadOnlyPermission()` (lines 54-65), remove from module.exports. Remove `normalizePermId()` (lines 20-24) ONLY if nothing else uses it — check pages.js step 1 first. If pages.js uses `hasReadOnlyPermission` inline instead, can inline the `.ro` check there and delete everything from authorize.js.'}
