2026-02-26 08:21:42,325 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_new args={'name': 'modal-plugin', 'title': 'Modal Plugin — auto-form, native dialog API, replace EUI shims', 'steps': ['Create modal-plugin.js — core plugin with $.fn.modal, open/close, data-action button wiring, callbacks', 'Alias $.fn.dialog and $.fn.window to $.fn.modal — backward compat', 'Move dynDialog into modal-plugin.js — keep old shim, use $.modal.create() underneath', 'Update +modal mixin in feedback.pug — auto-generate form, detect existing manual form and skip', 'Update +dialog and +window aliases — pass through auto-form behaviour', 'Retire window-plugin.js and dialog-plugin.js — remove from bundle', 'Update docs/dui/modal.md — new API, auto-form, form ID convention, data-action pattern', 'Update UI Help page — Modal component examples and output', 'Test across pages — datagrid editor, print dialog, part generator, dynDialog pages', 'Deferred: migrate existing pages to new modal pattern']}
2026-02-26 08:21:52,683 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': "Create a proper DUI modal plugin and update the +modal mixin to be a complete editing container.\n\n**Auto-include +form** — Every modal is used for editing data, so a form wrapper should be built in. Authors just drop in +fitem fields. Mixin detects if a manual form already exists in the block and skips the auto-generated one — existing code keeps working.\n\n**Form ID convention** — Auto-generate form id as {modalId}-form (e.g. #mymodal → #mymodal-form). Predictable, zero config.\n\n**Create modal-plugin.js** — Proper DUI plugin to replace the EUI $.fn.dialog / $.fn.window shims. Manages: open/close on native `<dialog>`, footer button clicks via data-action attributes with callbacks (onSave, onClose, onOpen), access to the auto-generated form, form validation on save.\n\n**Backward compat aliases** — $.fn.dialog and $.fn.window become aliases for $.fn.modal. All existing page scripts keep working unchanged.\n\n**Replace dynDialog** — Move dynDialog(vars, buts) into modal plugin as $.modal.create(opts). Old dynDialog shim stays — routes to new plugin internally, signature unchanged. Three pages use it: wo_bas.inc.js, sysbut.js, logins.js.\n\n**Retire old plugins** — Remove window-plugin.js and dialog-plugin.js from bundle.\n\n**Update pug mixin aliases** — +dialog and +window pass through auto-form behaviour.\n\n**#_fragments_ mount point** — $.modal.create() needs a mount point for dynamic modals.\n\n**No breaking changes** — Everything new is opt-in. Existing modals with manual forms, $.fn.dialog/$.fn.window calls, and dynDialog all keep working as-is.\n\n**Impact on existing pug templates:**\n- datagrid.pug — No manual form → auto-form is a bonus\n- print.pug — Has manual form#pops → continues working, auto-form skipped\n- _pn_gen_inc.pug — Has manual form → continues working, auto-form skipped\n\n**Update documentation** — docs/dui/modal.md and UI Help page.\n\n**Deferred: migrate existing pages** — Convert existing modals to new pattern gradually.\n\n**Result:**\n```pug\n+modal#mymodal(title='Edit Item')\n  +fitem('Name', {class:'textbox', name:'NAME'})\n  +modal-footer\n    +button('Save', {color:'primary', size:'sm', data-action:'save'})\n```\nForm wrapper automatic, Cancel auto-appended by +modal-footer, button actions managed by modal plugin."}
2026-02-26 08:21:58,909 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '1. Create modal-plugin.js — core plugin with $.fn.modal, open/close on native <dialog>, data-action button wiring, onSave/onClose/onOpen callbacks, form validation before save\n2. Alias $.fn.dialog and $.fn.window to $.fn.modal — backward compat, verify existing calls still work\n3. Move dynDialog into modal-plugin.js — keep old dynDialog shim routing to new internals, use $.modal.create() underneath\n4. Update +modal mixin in feedback.pug — auto-generate <form id="{modalId}-form"> inside modal-box, detect existing manual form and skip if present\n5. Update +dialog and +window aliases — pass through auto-form behaviour\n6. Retire window-plugin.js and dialog-plugin.js — remove from bundle\n7. Update docs/dui/modal.md — new API, auto-form, form ID convention, data-action pattern\n8. Update UI Help page — Modal component examples and output to match\n9. Test across pages — verify datagrid editor, print dialog, part generator, dynDialog pages all still work\n10. (Deferred) Migrate existing pages — convert manual form/footer patterns to new modal API'}
