2026-02-26 11:17:11,245 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': '**Remove the root cause — `req.query._udata` injection**\n\n- `lib/pages.js:190` — delete `req.query._udata = udata;`\n  - `res.locals.udata = udata` is already set at line 186 — pug templates access `udata` via locals\n- `lib/helpers.js:79-80` — delete the re-injection block:\n  ```\n  if (!req.query._udata && pugData.req && pugData.req.query && pugData.req.query._udata) {\n    req.query._udata = pugData.req.query._udata;\n  }\n  ```\n  - This was propagating the contamination from pugData back into req — no longer needed'}
2026-02-26 11:17:15,664 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': '**Update sa_parts.pug to use res.locals.udata instead of req.query._udata**\n\n3 files, same change on each:\n- `html/dui/mod/inv/sa_parts.pug:26` — `locals.req.query._udata.groups` → `locals.udata.groups`\n- `html/dui/x_mod.src/inv/sa_parts.pug:23` — same change\n- `html/eui/inv/sa_parts.pug:23` — same change (EUI frozen reference, but keeps consistency)\n\nAll check `PART-UD` group membership to conditionally show UDF tab.'}
2026-02-26 11:17:18,054 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': '**Remove the band-aid `delete query._udata` from proxyStream**\n\n- `lib/endpoints.js:259-260` — delete the comment and `delete query._udata;` line\n- With step 1 done, `_udata` is never on `req.query`, so this guard is dead code\n- Removing it keeps the codebase clean and prevents false confidence that band-aids are sufficient'}
