2026-02-26 13:28:12,980 2264818 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': "inv_gpass.pug:13 — `+fitem('Cust / Vendor ID',{id:'~', name:'GP_TYPE_ID', class:'combobox', required:true})`\nThe field name is GP_TYPE_ID, widget type is combobox. No static data or _sqlid defined in the template — it relies entirely on JS initialization for its options."}
2026-02-26 13:28:18,003 2264818 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_done args={'number': 2}
