2026-02-26 19:39:43,412 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_new args={'name': 'rest-api', 'title': 'REST API layer — Pure4 speaks standard CRUD, apiv4 translates to Pure3d', 'steps': ['Audit current Pure4→Pure3d communication — map all endpoints.js calls and their _sqlid/_func patterns', 'Design REST route structure — resource naming, HTTP methods, URL patterns, request/response format', 'Extend apiv4.js with REST routes — GET/POST/PUT/DELETE handlers that translate to _sqlid/_func', 'Refactor Pure4 endpoints.js — replace Basic Auth proxy with REST calls to apiv4', 'Test all CRUD operations — gatepass save, part master, combobox lookups, datagrid loads', 'Remove debug logging and Basic Auth code from endpoints.js']}
2026-02-26 19:39:49,572 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': "Replace Pure4's direct _sqlid/_func proxy (Basic Auth, raw query string building) with standard REST CRUD calls to apiv4.js on Pure3d. Pure4 sends normal HTTP methods + JSON bodies, apiv4 translates to Pure3d internals. This decouples Pure4 from Pure3d conventions and eliminates the userid/passwd injection bug. Later phase: browser AJAX also switches to REST style, eliminating endpoint translation in Pure4 entirely."}
2026-02-26 19:39:53,615 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': 'Architecture:\n- Pure4 (endpoints.js) → REST calls → apiv4.js (Pure3d) → _sqlid/_func internal handlers\n- REST routes: GET /api/:resource, POST /api/:resource, PUT /api/:resource/:id, DELETE /api/:resource/:id\n- apiv4 maps resource names to _sqlid values (e.g. "gatepass" → "inv^gp_head")\n- Token auth via X-Api-Key header (existing _pure4ui key)\n- Keep existing POST /api as backwards-compatible catch-all during transition\n- Phase 1: Pure4→Pure3d communication only\n- Phase 2 (later): Browser→Pure4 AJAX also uses REST, eliminates proxy translation'}
2026-02-26 19:40:09,068 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_checkpoint args={'message': 'before rest-api audit'}
2026-02-26 19:40:09,073 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.git running: git status --porcelain
2026-02-26 19:40:09,089 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.git git status --porcelain completed in 0.0s (rc=0)
2026-02-26 19:40:51,661 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': '## Audit: All Pure4 → Pure3d communication paths\n\n### 1. endpoints.js — processSqlIdRequest (HTTPS proxy with Basic Auth)\nAll requests go through this single function. It:\n- Merges query + body params\n- Splits _ prefixed args (remote URL query) from data fields (remote POST body)\n- Injects `_pure4ui` key for `admin^_` endpoints\n- Sends via HTTPS with Basic Auth header to `HOST/?_sqlid=...&_func=...`\n\n### 2. endpoints.js — proxyStream (binary stream proxy)\n- Streams report output (PDF/Excel) from `_func=penta` etc.\n- Uses Basic Auth, passes all query params as-is\n\n### Callers of processSqlIdRequest:\n\n**A. helpers.js — preLoad() [startup only]**\n- `_sqlid=admin^_globs, _func=get` → fetches global.$ config\n- Called ONCE at server start\n\n**B. uauth.js — loginHandler [login only]**\n- `_sqlid=admin^_udata, _func=get, _userid=X, _passwd=Y` → authenticate user\n- Called on POST /login\n\n**C. uauth.js — agentTokenMiddleware [token login only]**\n- `_sqlid=admin^_udata, _func=get, _userid=X` → fetch udata (no password)\n- Called ONCE per token login session\n\n**D. routes/proxy.js — sqlid middleware [every browser AJAX request]**\n- Passes browser req directly to processSqlIdRequest\n- _sqlid values: ANY — whatever the browser sends (inv^partall, inv^gp_head, etc.)\n- _func values: get, upd, ins, del\n- This is the HIGH VOLUME path — all datagrid loads, combobox lookups, form saves\n\n**E. routes/proxy.js — func middleware [report requests]**\n- Passes browser req to proxyStream\n- _func values: penta, excel, etc.\n\n### Summary of _sqlid/_func patterns:\n| Caller | _sqlid | _func | Volume |\n|--------|--------|-------|--------|\n| preLoad | admin^_globs | get | once at startup |\n| loginHandler | admin^_udata | get | per login |\n| agentToken | admin^_udata | get | per token login |\n| proxy.sqlid | ANY (browser) | get/upd/ins/del | every AJAX call |\n| proxy.func | n/a | penta/excel/etc | report downloads |\n\n### Key observation:\nOnly callers A-C use mock requests. Caller D passes the real Express req object — this is what we need to change to REST calls. But D also needs authorize() checks and session-based _appid resolution which are Pure4-specific (not Pure3d concerns).'}
2026-02-26 19:40:55,013 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_done args={'number': 1}
2026-02-26 19:42:20,822 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_switch args={'number': 2}
2026-02-26 19:52:37,254 2119379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': '## REST Route Design — Approved\n\n### CRUD routes\n```\nGET    /api/data/:module/:resource            → _func=get (read/query)\nGET    /api/data/:module/:resource/:id        → _func=get (single record)\nPOST   /api/data/:module/:resource            → _func=ins (create)\nPUT    /api/data/:module/:resource/:id        → _func=upd (update)\nDELETE /api/data/:module/:resource/:id        → _func=del (delete)\n```\napiv4 joins module+resource: `inv` + `partall` → `_sqlid=inv^partall`\n\n### Special endpoints\n```\nGET    /api/globs                → admin^_globs (global config)\nGET    /api/udata/:userid        → admin^_udata refresh\nPOST   /api/udata                → admin^_udata authenticate\nGET    /api/siteids              → admin^_siteids\n```\n\n### Reports\n```\nGET    /api/report?...           → binary stream proxy (PDF/Excel)\n```\n\n### Auth\n- X-Api-Key header with existing _pure4ui token (W336ZLKs)\n\n### Request format\n- GET: data fields as query params\n- POST/PUT/DELETE: data fields as JSON body\n- Additional _ options (_appid, _vpath, _docfiles) as query params\n\n### Verified\nAll known _sqlid values follow module^resource pattern — 100% compatible.'}
