2026-02-27 09:02:49,557 2334379 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'text': "DRY refactor opportunities in input/fitem mixins:\n\n1. COMBOBOX TEMPLATE DUPLICATION: The select+editbox+qbe template is copy-pasted 3 times in +input (hasNavi, hasQbe, plain branches — lines 185-220). Collapsing to one block with conditional navi/qbe buttons saves ~11 lines and eliminates triple-maintenance.\n\n2. TYPE DETECTION DUPLICATION: +fitem (form.pug:160-184) and +input (input.pug:56-141) both parse the class string to detect input type independently. Extract to a shared `detectInputType(cls)` helper function in helpers.pug — single source of truth, called from both mixins. ~30 lines of duplicated detection in +fitem eliminated.\n\n3. ID RESOLUTION DUPLICATION: Both +fitem (lines 150-158) and +input (line 20) do the same id='~'/name-as-id logic. Extract to a shared `resolveInputId(input)` helper function in helpers.pug."}
