2026-02-27 15:22:42,603 49563 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'transactions-editor-background-colour-investigation', 'kind': 'plan', 'text': '1. Reproduce the issue across relevant scenarios (new/edit/view, theme, user role, browser) and capture screenshots plus computed-style evidence.\n2. Define expected background-colour behavior from existing UI rules/tokens and record a clear pass/fail baseline.\n3. Trace style origin and precedence (template classes, CSS selectors, variables, inline styles, dynamic class toggles).\n4. Correlate mismatch cases with runtime state changes and identify the precise trigger conditions.\n5. Form and test root-cause hypotheses using non-invasive inspection only (no code edits).\n6. Propose rectification options ordered by safety and impact, including rollback considerations.\n7. Validate the preferred option against a scenario matrix and document acceptance criteria.\n8. Publish a final recommendation with step-by-step implementation guidance for a follow-up coding task.'}
