2026-02-27 15:27:37,410 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'patch-260227d — JS manual-warning detection rules for EUI patterns', 'description': 'Add detection rules to js-fixers.js that flag EUI patterns as js_manual warnings. These are NOT auto-fixes — they just ensure the migrator identifies them for manual review.\n\n## Patterns to detect (all go into manualWarnings):\n\n1. **`tbar.dgre_xxx`** — regex: `/\\.tbar\\.dgre_/` \n   Message: "EUI datagrid toolbar access — DUI uses #&lt;dgId&gt;_add/_edit/_del buttons"\n   Count: 90 occurrences across 20 files\n\n2. **`.rowEditor()`** — regex: `/\\.rowEditor\\s*\\(/`\n   Message: "EUI rowEditor() — DUI uses JSON config + editor modal"\n   Count: 0 currently but should be caught if encountered\n\n3. **Inline `columns:[[` in JS** — regex: `/columns\\s*:\\s*\\[\\[/`\n   Message: "Inline datagrid columns in JS — should be in datagrid.&lt;id&gt;.json"\n   Catches pages like inv_gpass.js that define full column configs in JS\n\n4. **`.datagrid(\'editButs\'`** — regex: `/\\.datagrid\\s*\\(\\s*[\'"]editButs/`\n   Message: "EUI editButs — DUI uses asdpx in JSON config"\n\n5. **`#_dgform` with no dgIds** — extend existing Transform 6 to also flag when dgIds array is empty (currently only flags multi-datagrid)\n\n## NOT flagged (working shims exist):\n- butEn() → window.butEn shim works\n- ajaxget() → window.ajaxget shim works  \n- clone() → window.clone from utils.js works\n- .linkbutton() → linkbutton-plugin.js works'}
