2026-02-27 15:32:08,502 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': "## Files\n- Page: html/dui/mod/inv/inv_gpass.pug (clean, no issues)\n- JS: html/dui/mod/inv/js/inv_gpass.js (8 manual warnings)\n- JSON: html/dui/mod/inv/json/datagrid.gplines.json (exists, basic columns)\n- YAML: scripts/migrator/mod/inv/inv_gpass.yaml (locked, owner: root)\n\n## Key DUI equivalents\n- `$('#dgid').datagrid('options').tbar.dgre_add` → `$('#gplines_add')` (button ID)\n- `.linkbutton('enable')` → `.linkbutton('enable')` (still works via linkbutton-plugin.js)\n- `.linkbutton('disable')` → `.linkbutton('disable')` (still works)\n- butEn(), ajaxget(), clone() — all have working window shims, no change needed\n\n## Approach\n1. Replace all 7 tbar.dgre_ references with direct button ID selectors (#gplines_add, #gplines_edit)\n2. The inline columns:[[]] in JS (L50-232) contains complex onSelect/onEndEdit callbacks that the JSON config can't handle — need to keep the callbacks in JS but move static column defs to JSON. This is the hardest part.\n3. Remove .rowEditor() call (L284) — DUI auto-wires via JSON asdpx\n4. Fix .texbox() typo (L323) → .textbox()\n5. Test in browser with real data"}
