2026-02-27 15:32:24,860 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': 'L50-232: Full datagrid opts object defined in JS with columns:[[...]], including:\n- Complex onSelect callbacks in DOC_ID qbe editor (L104-146) that populate PART_ID, PART_DESCRIPTION, QTY etc from SO/WO lookups\n- onSelect in PART_ID qbe editor (L194-198) that sets PART_DESCRIPTION and PART_UOM\n- onEndEdit (L223-228) that saves row via ajaxget to inv^gpline\n- onSelect (L229-231) that disables edit button when DOC_ID exists\n- onBeforeLoad (L216-218) guard on GP_ID\n- loadFilter (L219-222)\n- addData with $autonum and #GP_ID references (L62-65)\n\ndatagrid.gplines.json already has the basic column defs but WITHOUT callbacks.\n\nOptions:\nA) Keep all in JS, remove JSON config (simplest, but loses server-rendered headers)\nB) Keep JSON for static columns, merge callbacks from JS at runtime via datagrid options\nC) Move everything to JSON where possible, keep only callbacks in JS\n\nRecommend B — JSON provides columns for server-render, JS merges callbacks after init.'}
