2026-02-27 16:08:25,307 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'text': '## Initial Translation Map Entries (to seed docs/dui/migration-map.yaml)\n\n```yaml\npatterns:\n  ajaxget:\n    match: "ajaxget("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: "$.dui.ajax()"\n    notes: "shim exists via window.ajaxget, works but deprecated"\n\n  clone:\n    match: "clone("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "window.clone exists in utils.js, works as-is"\n\n  loadpage:\n    match: "loadpage("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  isronly:\n    match: "isronly("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  getapp:\n    match: "getapp("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  tbar_dgre:\n    match: ".tbar.dgre_"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    notes: "DUI creates #<dgId>_add/_edit/_del buttons. Datagrid plugin manages via tbarEnable/tbarDisable. _sink Proxy absorbs these calls silently (no-ops) but the code is dead."\n\n  linkbutton_enable:\n    match: ".linkbutton(\'enable\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: toolbar-plugin / datagrid-plugin\n    notes: "toolbar and datagrid plugins manage button state. Pages must NEVER call this."\n\n  linkbutton_disable:\n    match: ".linkbutton(\'disable\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: toolbar-plugin / datagrid-plugin\n    notes: "same as above"\n\n  butEn:\n    match: "butEn("\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: form-plugin\n    notes: "form state machine controls button enable/disable. Window shim exists but is intercepted when form state machine is active."\n\n  _dgform_selector:\n    match: "#_dgform"\n    action: translate\n    dui: "#<dgId>_editor"\n    notes: "replace #_dgform with actual datagrid ID + _editor suffix"\n\n  textboxname:\n    match: "textboxname="\n    action: translate\n    dui: "name="\n    notes: "EUI used textboxname attr, DUI uses standard name attr"\n\n  columns_inline:\n    match: "columns:[["\n    action: translate\n    dui: "datagrid.<id>.json"\n    notes: "move column definitions to JSON config file"\n\n  rowEditor:\n    match: ".rowEditor("\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    notes: "DUI uses JSON config + editor modal"\n\n  editButs:\n    match: ".datagrid(\'editButs\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    notes: "DUI uses asdpx in JSON/pug config"\n\n  dwap_page_loadData_def:\n    match: "$.page.fn.loadData ="\n    action: translate\n    dui: "$.page.register({ hooks: { afterLoad: function(data){...} }})"\n    notes: "migrator converts call-sites but NOT the definition. Must register loadData as afterLoad hook."\n```'}
2026-02-27 16:08:48,569 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'text': "## DUI Plugin Ownership Reference\n\n### form-plugin.js (47KB)\n- Manages main toolbar buttons: #but_add, #but_save, #but_del, #but_cancel\n- State machine: idle → loading → view → edit → saving (and transitions)\n- butEn() calls from pages are intercepted when state machine is active\n- Form lifecycle events: loadDone, done, changed, success\n- asdpx attribute on form controls which buttons are shown (a=add, s=save, d=delete, x=cancel)\n\n### datagrid-plugin.js (26KB)\n- Manages datagrid toolbar buttons: #<dgId>_add, #<dgId>_edit, #<dgId>_del\n- Buttons are plain <button> elements, NOT linkbuttons\n- tbarEnable()/tbarDisable() toggle CSS classes: opacity-40 pointer-events-none\n- opts.tbar defaults to a Proxy (_sink) that absorbs any property access silently — so EUI code calling opts.tbar.dgre_xxx.linkbutton() no-ops without error but is dead code\n- Column definitions should be in datagrid.<id>.json, not inline JS\n- Editor modal managed by plugin, not page\n\n### toolbar-plugin.js\n- Renders .tbut buttons from pug\n- butEn(mask) enables/disables buttons by asdpx character mask\n- When form state machine is active, page butEn() calls are gated/ignored\n\n### linkbutton-plugin.js\n- .linkbutton('enable'/'disable') for .tbut buttons checks $.dui.asdpx\n- For non-tbut buttons: removes/adds disabled attr and opacity classes\n- Datagrid toolbar buttons are NOT linkbutton-initialized\n\n### page-plugin.js\n- $.page.ready(fn) — replaces $(document).ready(), invokes fn immediately\n- $.page.fn — namespace for page-specific functions\n- $.page.register({ hooks: {...}, fn: {...} }) — registers hooks and functions\n- $.page.hook(name, ...args) — invokes registered hook by name\n- Hook registry is PRIVATE — only accessible via register()\n- afterLoad hooks fire when form loads a record — used to trigger datagrid loading\n\n### ajax-plugin.js\n- $.dui.ajax() — the proper DUI ajax call\n- window.ajaxget shim exists via dui.shim('ajaxget', ajaxget) — deprecated but functional\n\n## Current state of inv_gpass.js\n- User reformatted the file (prettier-style)\n- $.page.register({ hooks: { afterLoad: fn }}) applied — NOT YET TESTED SUCCESSFULLY\n- All button management stripped (butEn, linkbutton enable/disable, tbar.dgre_)\n- .rowEditor() removed\n- .texbox() typo fixed to .textbox()\n- Inline columns still in JS (step 2 of manual-sa-gpass task — not started)\n- The manual-sa-gpass task is mid-flight — steps 1,3,4 marked done but step 5 (browser test) incomplete"}
2026-02-27 16:11:40,864 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'id': 452, 'text': '## Initial Translation Map Entries (to seed docs/dui/migration-map.yaml)\n\nStructure note: each entry should have a `see_also` field pointing to the relevant docs/dui/*.md file for full API reference.\n\n```yaml\npatterns:\n  ajaxget:\n    match: "ajaxget("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: "$.dui.ajax()"\n    see_also: docs/dui/ajax.md\n    notes: "shim exists via window.ajaxget, works but deprecated"\n\n  clone:\n    match: "clone("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "window.clone exists in utils.js, works as-is"\n\n  loadpage:\n    match: "loadpage("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  isronly:\n    match: "isronly("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  getapp:\n    match: "getapp("\n    action: alias\n    shim: true\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  tbar_dgre:\n    match: ".tbar.dgre_"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "DUI creates #<dgId>_add/_edit/_del buttons. Datagrid plugin manages via tbarEnable/tbarDisable. _sink Proxy absorbs these calls silently (no-ops) but the code is dead."\n\n  linkbutton_enable:\n    match: ".linkbutton(\'enable\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: toolbar-plugin / datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/button.md\n    notes: "toolbar and datagrid plugins manage button state. Pages must NEVER call this."\n\n  linkbutton_disable:\n    match: ".linkbutton(\'disable\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: toolbar-plugin / datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/button.md\n    notes: "same as above"\n\n  butEn:\n    match: "butEn("\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: form-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/toolbar.md\n    notes: "form state machine controls button enable/disable. Window shim exists but is intercepted when form state machine is active."\n\n  _dgform_selector:\n    match: "#_dgform"\n    action: translate\n    dui: "#<dgId>_editor"\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "replace #_dgform with actual datagrid ID + _editor suffix"\n\n  textboxname:\n    match: "textboxname="\n    action: translate\n    dui: "name="\n    notes: "EUI used textboxname attr, DUI uses standard name attr"\n\n  columns_inline:\n    match: "columns:[["\n    action: translate\n    dui: "datagrid.<id>.json"\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "move column definitions to JSON config file"\n\n  rowEditor:\n    match: ".rowEditor("\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "DUI uses JSON config + editor modal"\n\n  editButs:\n    match: ".datagrid(\'editButs\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "DUI uses asdpx in JSON/pug config"\n\n  dwap_page_loadData_def:\n    match: "$.page.fn.loadData ="\n    action: translate\n    dui: "$.page.register({ hooks: { afterLoad: function(data){...} }})"\n    notes: "migrator converts call-sites but NOT the definition. Must register loadData as afterLoad hook."\n\n# When encountering an unknown EUI call:\n# 1. Check docs/dui/*.md files FIRST for the DUI equivalent\n# 2. Check public/dui/js/plugins/ source for shims (grep for dui.shim)\n# 3. If not found in either, classify as \'missing\' and add to this map\n```'}
