2026-02-27 16:14:53,753 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'id': 452, 'text': '## Initial Translation Map Entries (to seed docs/dui/migration-map.yaml)\n\n### Structure rules:\n- Each entry has a `see_also` field pointing to relevant docs/dui/*.md\n- Shim field is an object: { exists: bool, name: string, registered_in: string }\n- All shims MUST be registered via $.dui.shim() — no random global aliases\n- The YAML is the single source of truth for what shims exist and where they live\n- When action is \'translate\' and a shim is the right interim step: add it to $.dui.shim() in the appropriate plugin, register it in this YAML\n\n### When encountering an unknown EUI call:\n1. Check docs/dui/*.md files FIRST for the DUI equivalent\n2. Check public/dui/js/plugins/ source for existing shims (grep for dui.shim)\n3. If not found in either, classify as \'missing\' and add to this map\n4. If a shim is needed, add it via $.dui.shim() in the correct plugin and record it here\n\n```yaml\npatterns:\n  ajaxget:\n    match: "ajaxget("\n    action: alias\n    shim:\n      exists: true\n      name: ajaxget\n      registered_in: ajax-plugin.js\n    dui: "$.dui.ajax()"\n    see_also: docs/dui/ajax.md\n    notes: "shim exists via $.dui.shim, works but deprecated"\n\n  clone:\n    match: "clone("\n    action: alias\n    shim:\n      exists: true\n      name: clone\n      registered_in: utils.js\n    dui: null\n    notes: "window.clone exists in utils.js, works as-is"\n\n  loadpage:\n    match: "loadpage("\n    action: alias\n    shim:\n      exists: true\n      name: loadpage\n      registered_in: nav-plugin.js\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  isronly:\n    match: "isronly("\n    action: alias\n    shim:\n      exists: true\n      name: isronly\n      registered_in: form-plugin.js\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  getapp:\n    match: "getapp("\n    action: alias\n    shim:\n      exists: true\n      name: getapp\n      registered_in: page-plugin.js\n    dui: null\n    notes: "shim exists, deprecated warning shown"\n\n  tbar_dgre:\n    match: ".tbar.dgre_"\n    action: deprecated\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "DUI creates #<dgId>_add/_edit/_del buttons. _sink Proxy absorbs calls silently (no-ops) but code is dead. Remove entirely."\n\n  linkbutton_enable:\n    match: ".linkbutton(\'enable\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: toolbar-plugin / datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/button.md\n    notes: "plugins manage button state. Pages must NEVER call this. Remove entirely."\n\n  linkbutton_disable:\n    match: ".linkbutton(\'disable\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: toolbar-plugin / datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/button.md\n    notes: "same as linkbutton_enable"\n\n  butEn:\n    match: "butEn("\n    action: deprecated\n    shim:\n      exists: true\n      name: butEn\n      registered_in: toolbar-plugin.js\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: form-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/toolbar.md\n    notes: "shim exists but is intercepted/gated when form state machine is active. Remove from pages — plugin manages this."\n\n  _dgform_selector:\n    match: "#_dgform"\n    action: translate\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: "#<dgId>_editor"\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "replace #_dgform with actual datagrid ID + _editor suffix"\n\n  textboxname:\n    match: "textboxname="\n    action: translate\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: "name="\n    notes: "EUI used textboxname attr, DUI uses standard name attr"\n\n  columns_inline:\n    match: "columns:[["\n    action: translate\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: "datagrid.<id>.json"\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "move column definitions to JSON config file"\n\n  rowEditor:\n    match: ".rowEditor("\n    action: deprecated\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "DUI uses JSON config + editor modal. Remove entirely."\n\n  editButs:\n    match: ".datagrid(\'editButs\')"\n    action: deprecated\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: null\n    managed_by: datagrid-plugin\n    see_also: docs/dui/datagrid.md\n    notes: "DUI uses asdpx in JSON/pug config. Remove entirely."\n\n  dwap_page_loadData_def:\n    match: "$.page.fn.loadData ="\n    action: translate\n    shim:\n      exists: false\n    dui: "$.page.register({ hooks: { afterLoad: function(data){...} }})"\n    notes: "migrator converts call-sites but NOT the definition. Must register loadData as afterLoad hook."\n```'}
