2026-02-27 16:25:28,585 58002 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': "Expected behavior baseline: date filter bar (`#tbar` with From/To/Part ID) must appear at the top of the right-side center panel, directly above the transaction grid content. Legacy EUI and DUI source variants both rely on `toolbar:'#tbar'` in JS (`html/eui/inv/js/part_trans_editor.js:3`, `html/dui/x_mod.src/inv/js/part_trans_editor.js:3`) and define `#tbar` in page template (`.../part_trans_editor.pug:12`), implying toolbar should be attached as a grid header/toolbar rather than remain as trailing sibling below a flex-growing grid container. Acceptance baseline: top-visible on initial load, controls usable, table remains below filter bar across normal viewport sizes."}
