2026-02-27 16:25:42,512 58002 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': 'Template/layout trace:\n- Page center panel currently orders children as `+datagrid#txgrid` then `#tbar` (`html/dui/mod/inv/part_trans_editor.pug:11-13`).\n- Layout panel body is a vertical flex container (`html/dui/mixins/layout.pug:247-252`, classes include `flex-1 min-h-0 flex flex-col`).\n- Datagrid mixin root includes `flex-1` (`html/dui/mixins/datagrid.pug:75`), so `#txgrid` expands and consumes available height.\nConsequence: when `#tbar` remains a sibling placed after the flex-growing grid element, it is rendered at the bottom of the center panel.'}
