2026-02-27 16:25:56,192 58002 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 4, 'text': "Runtime initialization trace:\n- Page JS initializes datagrid with legacy option `toolbar:'#tbar'` (`html/dui/mod/inv/js/part_trans_editor.js:5`).\n- DUI datagrid plugin binds toolbar only by naming convention: `state._toolbar = document.getElementById(id + '_toolbar')` (`public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js:157`), and returns when missing (`:160`).\n- Search confirms no plugin handling for `options.toolbar` selector (`public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js` has no `options.toolbar` usage).\n- Datagrid mixin only generates toolbar markup with id `${dgId}_toolbar` when `asdpx` is configured (`html/dui/mixins/datagrid.pug:43-46,56`).\nTherefore `toolbar:'#tbar'` is not attached/relocated by plugin and `#tbar` remains a standalone DOM block in page flow."}
