2026-02-27 16:26:06,358 58002 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 5, 'text': "Root-cause ranking (highest confidence first):\n1) Primary root cause: framework contract mismatch. Page still uses EasyUI-style `toolbar:'#tbar'` while DUI datagrid expects `${gridId}_toolbar` convention; plugin does not consume `options.toolbar`. Evidence: JS config line 5 vs plugin lines 157/160 and no `options.toolbar` handler.\n2) Secondary root cause: template ordering and flex layout interaction. In center panel, `+datagrid#txgrid` precedes `#tbar`; datagrid has `flex-1`; panel body is column flex, so `#tbar` is pushed to bottom.\n3) Symptom interpretation issue: bar is not absent in DOM; it is visible but misplaced. Evidence from browser snapshot and coordinates (`tbarTop == gridBottom`).\nRejected alternatives: CSS `display:none` (false), auth/menu gating (not indicated), fetch/data failure (irrelevant because filter controls are static markup)."}
