2026-02-27 16:26:19,916 58002 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 6, 'text': "Rectification options (no changes applied in this task):\nPreferred (page-level migration, lowest blast radius)\n1. In `html/dui/mod/inv/part_trans_editor.pug`, place `#tbar` before `+datagrid#txgrid` in center panel so filter bar is explicitly top-of-panel content.\n2. In `html/dui/mod/inv/js/part_trans_editor.js`, remove/ignore legacy `toolbar:'#tbar'` dependency and keep filtering through `frm2dic(form#gfilter)` + reload logic.\n3. Keep `#tbar` as page-owned filter strip (not datagrid toolbar contract), ensuring style classes are DUI-friendly if needed.\nFallback A (framework-level compatibility)\n1. Extend `public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js` to support `options.toolbar` selector semantics and relocate/anchor external toolbar element near table header.\n2. Validate all pages using datagrid for unintended side effects.\nFallback B (full DUI-native)\n1. Move filter controls into a dedicated top container separate from datagrid mixin toolbar concepts.\n2. Use datagrid built-in `_toolbar` only for CRUD buttons (`asdpx`) and keep query filters independent.\nRisk controls\n- Avoid changing plugin behavior unless necessary (high blast radius).\n- Add targeted regression checks on other inv/sales grids if plugin is touched.\nRollback\n- Revert page-level ordering/script change only (preferred path) if UI regressions appear."}
