2026-02-27 16:26:49,307 58002 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 8, 'text': "Implementation-ready investigation output (no code changes applied):\nProblem statement: top date filter bar on right side of Transactions Editor appears missing.\nObserved state: bar exists in DOM and is visible, but rendered below grid (bottom of panel).\nCode evidence:\n- Legacy toolbar option used: `html/dui/mod/inv/js/part_trans_editor.js:5` (`toolbar:'#tbar'`).\n- Template order places grid before filter bar: `html/dui/mod/inv/part_trans_editor.pug:11-13`.\n- Datagrid plugin toolbar contract uses `id + '_toolbar'`: `public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js:157`; early return if missing at `:160`; no `options.toolbar` support found.\n- Datagrid root is flex-growing element: `html/dui/mixins/datagrid.pug:75` (`flex-1`).\n- Panel body is column flex: `html/dui/mixins/layout.pug:247-252`.\nRoot cause:\n1. Contract mismatch between legacy EasyUI `toolbar:'#tbar'` and DUI datagrid plugin naming convention.\n2. Child ordering + flex growth pushes standalone `#tbar` to bottom.\nRectification sequence (preferred):\n1. Move `#tbar` above `+datagrid#txgrid` in center panel template.\n2. Remove reliance on legacy `toolbar:'#tbar'` in page JS; keep filtering via existing form query params + reload.\n3. Verify placement and filtering behavior with validation matrix from Step 7.\nAlternative sequence (higher risk): implement plugin support for `options.toolbar` selector.\nOutcome: root cause isolated with high confidence; ready for follow-up implementation task."}
