2026-02-27 18:54:49,162 14085 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 5, 'text': 'EUI Discovery:\n- Layout: west panel (410px, form#parttrans) + center panel (datagrid#txgrid with #tbar filter)\n- Record selector: date filter (From/To default to today via .today class) + Part ID combobox. onChange triggers datagrid reload.\n- Data: 58 rows when date range widened to 2020-01-01 → today. No data for today only.\n- Checkbox select: onCheck populates left form with row data + dynamically shows/hides trace user fields based on TRACE_USER_X_LBL columns\n- Dynamic labels: TRACE_USER_1_LBL → "OD", TRACE_USER_2_LBL → "THK", etc. Empty LBL = hidden field. * prefix = required.\n- Save: updates datagrid row client-side, then form submit with _func=upd, _sqlid=inv^part_trace\n\nDUI Issues identified:\n1. datebox.today not setting default dates → filter empty → datagrid won\'t load\n2. onCheck selector uses div.fitem#TRACE_USER_X_LBL but data key is TRACE_USER_X_LBL — need to verify this matches\n3. label.trace selector won\'t match DUI markup'}
