2026-02-28 07:59:49,949 98303 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## Naming Convention\n\nAll migration pipeline skills use `dui-` prefix. Pipeline order:\n\n1. `/dui-migrate` — run migrator script (was `/migrate-page`)\n2. `/dui-discover` — capture EUI baseline (was `/eui-discover`)\n3. `/dui-audit` — code audit against migration map (split from `/fix-migrated-page`)\n4. `/dui-fix` — apply fixes from audit (split from `/fix-migrated-page`)\n5. `/dui-verify` — functional verification against baseline (split from `/fix-migrated-page`)\n6. `/dui-layout` — visual/structural layout fixes (was `/fix-layout`)\n7. `/dui-fix-dgedit` — fix datagrid editor dialogs (was `/fix-dgedit`)\n8. `/dui-lint` — theme compliance check (was `/lint-theme`)\n\nNavigation utilities stay as-is: `/eui`, `/dui`, `/pure3d`\n\n## Auto-cascade\n\nEach skill checks its prerequisites and auto-invokes if missing:\n- `/dui-audit` → needs YAML (run `/dui-migrate`) + needs `eui_baseline` (run `/dui-discover`)\n- `/dui-fix` → needs audit findings (run `/dui-audit`)\n- `/dui-verify` → needs `eui_baseline` (run `/dui-discover`)\n- `/dui-layout` → needs `eui_baseline.layout_profile` (run `/dui-discover`)\n\n## Implementation\n\n1. Rename existing skills (directory + SKILL.md)\n2. Split `/fix-migrated-page` into `/dui-audit`, `/dui-fix`, `/dui-verify`\n3. Update cross-references in all skills\n4. Delete old skill directories'}
