2026-02-28 14:06:28,280 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 8, 'text': 'Changes needed:\n\n1. **datagrid.logins.json** — add toolbar array:\n   ```json\n   "toolbar": [\n     { "id": "but_user_msg", "text": "Message", "icon": "message-square", "disabled": true },\n     { "id": "but_user_logout", "text": "Logout", "icon": "log-out", "disabled": true }\n   ]\n   ```\n   (toolbar changes from `true` to an array — presence of array implies toolbar)\n\n2. **datagrid.pug mixin** — when `cfg.toolbar` is an array, iterate and render `+button` for each entry\n\n3. **datagrid-plugin.js** — `bindRowSelection`: enable/disable ALL buttons in toolbar div on select/unselect (not just asdpx _edit/_del)\n\n4. **logins.pug** — remove the block content buttons (they come from JSON now)\n\n5. **logins.js** — remove `toolbut()` call (lines 234-301), remove `linkbutton(\'enable\'/\'disable\')` calls (lines 37, 195, 200, 270), wire click handlers via `$(\'#but_user_msg\').on(\'click\', ...)` and `$(\'#but_user_logout\').on(\'click\', ...)`'}
