2026-02-28 14:56:47,131 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Strip duplicate datagrid config from JS + plugin column merge by field', 'description': 'After the migrator extracts datagrid configs to JSON, the JS still has the full duplicate config. Need to:\n\n1. Plugin change: deep-merge columns by `field` name (JSON structure + JS runtime functions)\n2. New script: `scripts/strip-dg-config.js` — removes declarative props from JS datagrid init calls when JSON config exists\n3. Migrator integration: call the stripper after extraction\n\nSee plan file for full details: /root/.claude/plans/quiet-inventing-muffin.md'}
2026-02-28 14:57:04,895 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': "## Plan\n\n### Part 1: Plugin column merge by field\n- In `datagrid-plugin.js` init path (~line 490), when both dataOpts and JS options have `columns`:\n- Build a map of JSON columns by `field` name\n- For each JS column, merge its function props (formatter, styler, sorter) onto the matching JSON column\n- Result: JSON provides structure (field, title, width, align, hidden), JS provides runtime (formatter, styler)\n- If JS has a column with no JSON match, keep it as-is (additive)\n\n### Part 2: Strip script (`scripts/strip-dg-config.js`)\n- For each `$('#id').datagrid({...})` call, check if JSON config exists\n- Strip declarative top-level props: url, queryParams, rownumbers, singleSelect, striped, fitColumns, fit, selectOnCheck, checkOnSelect, loadMsg, method, pagination, title, toolbar, pageSize, pageList, pagePosition, noWrap, autoRowHeight, showFooter, idField, remoteSort, remoteFilter, sortName, sortOrder\n- Strip declarative column props: title, width, align, hidden, checkbox, editor, order, halign, sortable, resizable, fixed, rowspan, colspan\n- Keep column `field` (always) + function props (formatter, styler, sorter)\n- Remove columns that have only `field` left (no functions)\n- Remove empty `columns` array, remove empty `.datagrid()` call\n- Supports `--dry-run` and `--all` flags\n\n### Part 3: Migrator integration\n- In `scripts/migrator/index.js` after extractor runs (~line 470), call the stripper\n\n### Execution order\n1. Plugin merge first (so stripped JS works)\n2. Create strip script\n3. Test on logins.js + browser verify\n4. Dry-run all 17 affected files\n5. Apply all + spot-check\n6. Wire into migrator\n\n### Files\n- `public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js` — column merge\n- NEW `scripts/strip-dg-config.js` — stripper\n- `scripts/migrator/index.js` — integration"}
