2026-02-28 16:05:53,776 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': '## EUI Tree Screenshots Captured\n\n### Files in `.pw/`:\n1. `eui-tree-admin-files.png` — Document Manager folder tree (Global/Modules/Site/System). Navigation tree with expand arrows and colored folder icons. No checkboxes.\n2. `eui-tree-admin-users-access.png` — User Manager Access tab. Checkbox tree with module categories (System, Company, Quality, Inventory, etc.). Each root node: expand arrow + module icon + checkbox + label.\n3. `eui-tree-admin-users-access-expanded.png` — Same tree with Inventory expanded. Child pages visible (Part Masters, Gate Pass, etc.). Mixed check states — some checked, some not. "Tool Room" has sub-children (branch node). Parent "Inventory" unchecked but children independently checked = cascadeCheck:false.\n4. `eui-tree-admin-users-groups.png` — Groups tab. **Three icons per leaf**: green checkmark OR red cross status icon + checkbox + label. Fully expanded. Shows per-module permission groups.\n5. `eui-tree-admin-users-events.png` — Events tab. Same 3-icon pattern as Groups.\n6. `eui-tree-admin-users-reports.png` — Reports tab. Same 3-icon pattern as Groups. Very long list per module.\n\n### Tree Types Identified:\n- **Navigation tree** (admin^files, admin^events, sidebar menu) — click to select/navigate, no checkboxes\n- **Checkbox tree** (admin^users Access tab) — checkboxes for toggling access, with cascadeCheck:false\n- **Checkbox + status icon tree** (admin^users Groups/Events/Reports tabs) — checkbox + ✓/✗ status icon showing current vs saved state\n\n### EUI Tree IDs on admin^users page:\n- `#adm_auth_t` — Access tree\n- `#reports` — Reports tree  \n- `#ugroups` — Groups tree\n- `#events` — Events tree\n- `#westMenu` — Sidebar navigation tree (separate from page trees)'}
