2026-02-28 16:08:21,314 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': '## Complete EUI Tree API Inventory\n\n### Methods (34 total)\n\n**Core (from $.fn.tree.methods):**\n| Method | Args | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| options | — | Get options object |\n| loadData | data | Load tree from array |\n| getNode | id | Get node by ID |\n| getData | id | Get node data by ID |\n| reload | nodeId? | Reload tree or branch |\n| getRoot | nodeEl? | Get root node |\n| getRoots | — | Get all root nodes |\n| getParent | nodeEl | Get parent node |\n| getChildren | nodeEl? | Get children |\n| getChecked | states? | Get checked nodes |\n| getSelected | — | Get selected node |\n| isLeaf | nodeEl | Check if leaf |\n| find | id | Find node by ID |\n| select | nodeEl | Select node |\n| check | nodeEl | Check checkbox |\n| uncheck | nodeEl | Uncheck checkbox |\n| collapse | nodeEl | Collapse node |\n| expand | nodeEl | Expand node |\n| collapseAll | nodeEl? | Collapse all |\n| expandAll | nodeEl? | Expand all |\n| expandTo | nodeEl | Expand ancestors |\n| scrollTo | nodeEl | Scroll to visible |\n| toggle | nodeEl | Toggle expand/collapse |\n| append | {parent,data} | Add children |\n| insert | {before/after,data} | Insert node |\n| remove | nodeEl | Remove node |\n| pop | nodeEl | Remove + return data |\n| update | {target,text,...} | Update properties |\n| enableDnd | — | Enable drag-drop |\n| disableDnd | — | Disable drag-drop |\n| beginEdit | nodeEl | Start inline edit |\n| endEdit | nodeEl | End edit + save |\n| cancelEdit | nodeEl | Cancel edit |\n| doFilter | text | Filter nodes |\n\n**Extended (eui.extend.js):**\n| Method | Args | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| getLevel | nodeEl | Node depth count |\n| getLeafs | — | All leaf nodes |\n| lock | node? | Lock selection |\n| unlock | node? | Unlock selection |\n| move | {target,dir} | Move up/down |\n| setIcon | {node,icon} | Set node icon |\n| clearIcon | {node,icon} | Remove node icon |\n| setFocus | nodeId | Select + expand to |\n\n### Options\n| Option | Type | Default | Description |\n|--------|------|---------|-------------|\n| url | String | null | AJAX load URL |\n| method | String | "post" | HTTP method |\n| animate | Boolean | false | Animate expand/collapse |\n| checkbox | Boolean | false | Show checkboxes |\n| cascadeCheck | Boolean | true | Parent checks cascade to children |\n| onlyLeafCheck | Boolean | false | Only leaves get checkboxes |\n| lines | Boolean | false | Show tree lines |\n| dnd | Boolean | false | Drag-and-drop |\n| data | Array | null | Initial data |\n| queryParams | Object | {} | Extra AJAX params |\n| formatter | Function | node=>node.text | Format display text |\n| filter | Function | — | Filter for doFilter() |\n| loader | Function | — | Custom AJAX loader |\n| loadFilter | Function | data=>data | Transform loaded data |\n\n### Events (24)\nonClick, onDblClick, onBeforeExpand, onExpand, onBeforeCollapse, onCollapse, onBeforeCheck, onCheck, onBeforeSelect, onSelect, onContextMenu, onBeforeLoad, onLoadSuccess, onLoadError, onBeforeDrag, onStartDrag, onStopDrag, onDragEnter, onDragOver, onDragLeave, onBeforeDrop, onDrop, onBeforeEdit, onAfterEdit, onCancelEdit\n\n### Node Properties\nid, text, target (DOM), children, checked, state (\'open\'/\'closed\'), iconCls, attributes (custom), cls\n\n### EUI DOM Structure\n```\nul.tree > li#id > div.tree-node > span.tree-hit + span.tree-indent + span.tree-icon + span.tree-checkbox + span.tree-title\n                > ul.tree-children (nested)\n```\n\n### Critical Pattern: node.target\nMost methods require `node.target` (DOM element), NOT the node object. Pattern: `tree(\'find\', id)` returns node, then `tree(\'select\', node.target)`.\n\n### Most-used patterns in codebase:\n1. find + select + expandTo (navigation)\n2. getChecked → build CSV (save checked items)\n3. loadData from AJAX response\n4. onSelect handler for data binding\n5. onCheck for permission toggle\n6. lock/unlock during bulk operations'}
