2026-02-28 16:13:23,552 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 4, 'text': "## Existing DUI Tree Skeleton Audit\n\n### tree-plugin.js (464 lines) — Sidebar-only, NOT generic\n\n**Hard-coupled to `#westMenu`:** `find()`, `getSelected()`, `select()`, `getRoots()` all query `$('#westMenu')` directly.\n\n**Working methods:** `loadData()`, `append()`, `update()`, `getLevel()`, `getParent()`, `isLeaf()`, `options()`\n**Stub/broken methods:** `getNode()` → null, `getData()` → null, `getChildren()` → [], `getChecked()` → [], `check()`/`uncheck()` → no-op, DnD stubs, editing stubs\n**Collapse/expand:** Uses crude `.hide()`/`.show()` instead of `<details>` open attribute\n\n**NOT registered:** No `$.dui.shim()` call, no `dui._plugins.loaded.push()`\n**No events:** Zero callbacks, purely imperative\n\n### No tree mixin exists\n- `html/dui/mixins/` has no tree.pug\n- `+menuItem()` in nav.pug is sidebar-specific, not reusable\n\n### No tree docs exist\n- `docs/dui/tree.md` does NOT exist\n\n### Assessment: Needs full rewrite\nThe existing plugin is a nav-sidebar widget, not a generic tree. For the DUI tree component we need:\n1. New generic plugin that works on ANY `ul.menu` tree element\n2. New pug mixin (`+tree`) for server-rendered trees\n3. `<template>` elements for dynamic node creation\n4. Proper event system matching EUI callbacks\n5. Checkbox support with cascade logic\n6. Registration via `$.dui.shim()`"}
