2026-02-28 16:13:54,500 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 5, 'text': '## Static Tree Mixin Design\n\n### Mixin File: `html/dui/mixins/tree.pug`\n\n### Mixins\n\n#### `+tree(opts)`\nContainer mixin. Renders `ul.menu` with optional id, size, checkbox mode.\n\n**opts:**\n| Opt | Type | Default | Description |\n|-----|------|---------|-------------|\n| id | String | — | Element ID (required for JS API) |\n| checkbox | Boolean | false | Enable checkbox mode |\n| cascadeCheck | Boolean | true | Cascade checks to children |\n| onlyLeafCheck | Boolean | false | Only leaves get checkboxes |\n| size | String | \'sm\' | menu-xs/sm/md/lg |\n| url | String | — | AJAX load URL (stored as data-url) |\n\n**Renders:**\n```pug\nul.menu.menu-sm(id=opts.id data-checkbox=opts.checkbox data-cascade-check=opts.cascadeCheck data-url=opts.url)&attributes(attributes)\n  block\n  template.tree-node-tpl\n    //- Template for dynamic node creation (used by JS API)\n    li\n      a\n        span.tree-icon.w-4.h-4.flex-shrink-0\n        span.tree-text\n```\n\nThe `<template>` inside the tree provides the node structure for `loadData()`, `append()`, and `insert()` methods. JS clones this template when creating nodes dynamically.\n\n#### `+tree-node(node)`\nRecursive node renderer for server-side data.\n\n**node properties:** `{ id, text, iconCls, children, checked, state, cls }`\n\n**Renders (leaf):**\n```pug\nli(id=node.id data-node-id=node.id)\n  if opts.checkbox\n    label.flex.items-center.gap-2.cursor-pointer\n      input.checkbox.checkbox-xs(type="checkbox" checked=node.checked)\n      if node.iconCls\n        span.w-4.h-4.flex-shrink-0(data-lucide=getIcon(node.iconCls))\n      span= node.text\n  else\n    a(data-node-id=node.id)\n      if node.iconCls\n        span.w-4.h-4.flex-shrink-0(data-lucide=getIcon(node.iconCls))\n      span= node.text\n```\n\n**Renders (branch with children):**\n```pug\nli(id=node.id data-node-id=node.id)\n  details(open=(node.state === \'open\'))\n    summary\n      if node.iconCls\n        span.w-4.h-4.flex-shrink-0(data-lucide=getIcon(node.iconCls))\n      span= node.text\n    ul.menu\n      each child in node.children\n        +tree-node(child)\n```\n\n### Usage Examples\n\n**Static navigation tree:**\n```pug\n+tree({id: \'fileTree\', size: \'sm\'})\n  +tree-node({id: \'global\', text: \'Global\', iconCls: \'icon-folder\', state: \'open\', children: [\n    {id: \'templates\', text: \'Templates\', iconCls: \'icon-file\'},\n    {id: \'reports\', text: \'Reports\', iconCls: \'icon-file\'}\n  ]})\n```\n\n**Dynamic tree (loaded via JS):**\n```pug\n+tree({id: \'accessTree\', checkbox: true, cascadeCheck: false, url: \'/?_sqlid=admin^users_access\'})\n```\n\n**Checkbox tree with server data:**\n```pug\n- var treeData = fn.pug.jsonRead(\'json/access-tree.json\')\n+tree({id: \'accessTree\', checkbox: true, cascadeCheck: false})\n  each node in treeData\n    +tree-node(node)\n```'}
