2026-02-28 16:15:22,555 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'id': 467, 'text': "## Goal: DUI Tree Component\n\nBuild a complete tree component for DUI that replaces EUI's `$.fn.tree` with 100% DaisyUI markup.\n\n### Deliverables\n1. **Pug mixin** (`html/dui/mixins/tree.pug`) — `+tree(opts)` and `+tree-node(node)` for server-rendered trees\n2. **JS plugin** (`public/dui/js/plugins/tree-plugin.js`) — full rewrite, generic tree API matching EUI method names\n3. **Documentation** (`docs/dui/tree.md`) — API reference with examples\n\n### Requirements\n- 100% DaisyUI `ul.menu` + `details/summary` markup — no custom tree classes\n- Same method names as EUI API (`find`, `select`, `expand`, `check`, `getChecked`, `loadData`, `append`, etc.)\n- `<template>` elements for dynamic node creation (consistent with datagrid/dynadd pattern)\n- Support all 3 tree variants: navigation, checkbox, checkbox+status icons\n- Generic plugin — works on ANY tree element, NOT hard-coupled to `#westMenu`\n- Proper event system: onSelect, onCheck, onExpand, onCollapse, onLoadSuccess, etc.\n\n### EUI Tree Usage (13+ pages)\n- admin/users: 4 checkbox trees (access, reports, groups, events) — cascadeCheck:false\n- admin/files: folder navigation tree with DnD\n- admin/events: navigation tree with onSelect\n- user/pref: event subscription checkbox tree\n- dqm/*: various checkbox and navigation trees\n- vwltsa/*: job/operation trees\n\n### Screenshots (in `.pw/`)\n- `eui-tree-admin-files.png` — folder tree (icons, expand arrows)\n- `eui-tree-admin-users-access.png` — checkbox tree (collapsed)\n- `eui-tree-admin-users-access-expanded.png` — checkbox tree (expanded, mixed checks)\n- `eui-tree-admin-users-groups.png` — checkbox + ✓/✗ status icons\n- `eui-tree-admin-users-events.png` — checkbox + status icons\n- `eui-tree-admin-users-reports.png` — checkbox + status icons\n\n### API Methods to Implement (Phase 1 — 28 methods)\n**Query:** find, getSelected, getNode, getData, getRoots, getRoot, getParent, getChildren, getLevel, isLeaf, getChecked, getLeafs, options\n**Selection:** select, lock, unlock, setFocus\n**Expand:** expand, collapse, toggle, expandAll, collapseAll, expandTo, scrollTo\n**Checkbox:** check, uncheck\n**Mutation:** loadData, append, insert, remove, pop, update, reload\n\n### Deferred (Phase 2)\nDnD, inline editing, doFilter, move"}
2026-02-28 16:15:40,727 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'id': 468, 'text': "## Implementation Plan\n\n### Research Phase (COMPLETE)\n1. ✅ EUI tree screenshots — 6 screenshots covering all tree variants\n2. ✅ EUI tree JS API — 34 core methods, 14 options, 24 events inventoried\n3. ✅ DaisyUI tree markup — ul.menu + details/summary pattern documented\n4. ✅ Existing DUI tree audit — hard-coupled to #westMenu, needs full rewrite\n5. ✅ Static mixin design — +tree(opts) + +tree-node(node) with <template>\n6. ✅ Dynamic JS API design — all 28 Phase 1 methods mapped to DUI DOM ops\n7. ✅ Comprehensive notes written\n\n### Build Phase (NEXT — create new steps when starting)\n\n**Step A: Pug mixin** (`html/dui/mixins/tree.pug`)\n- `+tree(opts)` container: ul.menu with data attrs + <template>\n- `+tree-node(node)` recursive: leaf (a/label) and branch (details/summary)\n- Checkbox mode, icon support, size variants\n- Test with static data in a dev page\n\n**Step B: Plugin core** (`public/dui/js/plugins/tree-plugin.js`)\n- Full rewrite — generic, works on any tree element\n- Node creation from <template> (createNode function)\n- $.data('tree-node') storage on each <li>\n- buildNodeObj() helper to create EUI-compatible node objects\n- Registration via $.dui.shim('tree')\n\n**Step C: Query methods**\n- find, getSelected, getNode, getData, getRoots, getRoot\n- getParent, getChildren, getLevel, isLeaf, getChecked, getLeafs\n\n**Step D: Action methods**\n- select (with .menu-active), lock/unlock, setFocus\n- expand/collapse/toggle/expandAll/collapseAll/expandTo/scrollTo\n- check/uncheck with cascade logic + indeterminate state\n\n**Step E: Mutation methods**\n- loadData, append, insert, remove, pop, update, reload (AJAX)\n\n**Step F: Event system**\n- Delegated click/dblclick/contextmenu handlers on tree container\n- details toggle event listener for expand/collapse\n- checkbox change listener for check/uncheck\n- All onBefore* callbacks support return false to cancel\n\n**Step G: Integration test**\n- Test with admin/users tree data (4 checkbox trees)\n- Test with admin/files folder tree\n- Verify in browser via dev page\n\n**Step H: Documentation**\n- Create docs/dui/tree.md with full API reference + examples + Output section\n\n### Key Files\n| File | Action |\n|------|--------|\n| `html/dui/mixins/tree.pug` | NEW — mixin |\n| `public/dui/js/plugins/tree-plugin.js` | REWRITE — plugin |\n| `docs/dui/tree.md` | NEW — documentation |\n| `scripts/build-dui-plugins.sh` | EDIT — add tree-plugin to bundle |"}
