2026-02-28 17:51:55,784 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_new args={'name': 'icon-standardize', 'title': 'Standardize icon handling across all DUI components — one convention, one code path', 'steps': ['Audit all mixins and document current icon handling (DONE — see audit)', 'Define the standard: property name, resolution, render pattern, sizes', 'Fix panel header — broken <i> tag, needs data-lucide', 'Fix modal titlebar — add getIcon() resolution', 'Fix datagrid title — add getIcon() resolution', 'Standardize icon sizes across components', 'Update dynamic node template in tree plugin to match', 'Verify all components render icons correctly in browser']}
2026-02-28 17:52:01,486 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Every DUI component that accepts an icon must use the SAME convention:\n- Property: `iconCls` (EUI-compatible name, accepted everywhere)\n- Resolution: always through `getIcon()` server-side, `$.dui.getIcon()` client-side\n- Render: `span(data-lucide=resolvedName)` with standard class pattern\n- Sizes: intentional per context (w-4 standard, w-5 nav menu, w-3.5 modal titlebar) but using a shared CSS class approach\n\nNo component invents its own icon handling. One code path for all.'}
2026-02-28 17:54:58,023 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': "## Plan\n\n### 1. Create shared `+icon` mixin\nIn `_iconmap.pug` (already included everywhere), add:\n```pug\nmixin icon(iconCls, opts)\n  - resolve via getIcon(), apply size/color, render span(data-lucide=...)\n```\nOptions: `size` (default 'w-4 h-4'), `color` (e.g. 'text-primary'), `cls` (extra classes), `opacity` (e.g. 'opacity-70')\n\n### 2. Create shared `$.dui.renderIcon(iconCls, opts)` JS function\nIn `dui-namespace.js`, add function that returns a DOM element (span with data-lucide). Same options as mixin. All plugins call this instead of building their own icon spans.\n\n### 3. Replace icon rendering in every component mixin\n- `tree.pug` — replace `span.w-4.h-4.flex-shrink-0(data-lucide=iconName)` with `+icon(iconName)`\n- `feedback.pug` (modal) — replace titlebar icon with `+icon(iconCls, {size: 'sm'})`, add getIcon() resolution\n- `layout.pug` (panel) — replace broken `i(class=iconCls)` with `+icon(iconCls)`\n- `datagrid.pug` — replace title icon with `+icon(cfg.iconCls, {opacity: 'opacity-70'})`\n- `nav.pug` — replace `+lucideIcon()` helper with `+icon()`, remove the old helper\n- `actions.pug` (button) — replace inline icon rendering with `+icon()`\n- `toolbar.pug` — replace hardcoded spans with `+icon('plus')` etc.\n\n### 4. Replace icon rendering in every plugin JS\n- `tree-plugin.js` — use `$.dui.renderIcon()` in createNodeEl()\n- `datagrid-plugin.js` — use it for toolbar button icons + title icon\n- `modal-plugin.js` — use it for titlebar + button icons\n- `nav-plugin.js` — use it if any dynamic icon creation exists\n\n### 5. Support iconColor in tree node data\nTree `cls` property currently colors the whole `<li>`. Instead, pass `iconColor` through to `+icon(iconCls, {color: iconColor})`.\n\n### 6. Rebuild CSS + plugins, test all components in browser"}
