2026-02-28 18:23:19,149 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_new args={'name': 'single-map', 'title': 'Single source of truth — unify migration map for migrator + skills', 'steps': ['Extend migration-map.yaml with widgets section (mixin, init, extract fields)', 'Create scripts/migrator/load-map.js — YAML loader with structured lookups', 'Refactor pug-fixers.js — replace 4 hardcoded maps with load-map lookups', 'Refactor skills to use load-map.js (or read same YAML sections)', 'Fix 17 pages — revert wrong +menu calls back to bare div', 'Test migrator on sample page — verify map-driven conversion matches old behavior']}
2026-02-28 18:23:23,836 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Eliminate duplicate/conflicting widget conversion maps. Currently the migrator (pug-fixers.js) has 4 hardcoded maps and the skills read docs/dui/migration-map.yaml — two sources of truth that diverge silently. This caused 17 pages to get wrong +menu conversions. Unify into one canonical YAML that both consume.'}
2026-02-28 18:23:37,803 268582 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': "## Plan\n\n### Step 1: Extend migration-map.yaml\nAdd `widgets` section with every EUI widget type. Fields per widget:\n- `mixin`: target mixin name or `null` (leave as bare element)\n- `init`: `server` (mixin renders it) or `js` (JS initializes it, don't touch DOM)\n- `extract`: `json` if static config should be extracted to JSON def file\n- `input_mixin`: for input-type widgets, the DUI mixin name\n\nWidgets to include (from the 4 hardcoded maps):\n- fixEasyuiWidgetDivs: tabs, datagrid, filegrid, treegrid, layout\n- easyui-class-on-tag: tabs, datagrid, filegrid, treegrid, layout, menu, form\n- fixBareInputWidgets: combobox, datebox, textbox, numberbox, numberspinner, validatebox\n- fixJsInitializedWidgets: datagrid, treegrid, propertygrid\n- Plus: tree, menu (both null/js)\n\n### Step 2: Create load-map.js\nSingle loader that reads migration-map.yaml and exposes:\n- `getWidgetMap()` → full widget section\n- `getWidgetMixin(name)` → mixin or null\n- `getJsInitWidgets()` → names where init=js (for regex in fixJsInitializedWidgets)\n- `getInputWidgets()` → input-type widget map\n- `getEasyuiClassMap()` → for easyui-class-on-tag fixer\n\n### Step 3: Refactor pug-fixers.js\nReplace all 4 inline maps with calls to load-map.js. Behavior must be identical — just the data source changes.\n\n### Step 4: Refactor skills\nSkills already read migration-map.yaml. Just ensure they use the `widgets` section for widget-related decisions (e.g. don't convert `menu` to `+menu`).\n\n### Step 5: Fix 17 pages\nRevert `+menu#id` → `div#id` (or `#id` with children) on all 17 affected DUI pages. Context menus are JS-owned — bare divs, hidden by default.\n\n### Step 6: Test\nRun migrator on a sample page, verify output matches expected behavior with map-driven lookups."}
