2026-03-01 12:57:51,029 416824 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'smart-migrate', 'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## Approach: AI-driven /dui-migrate skill\n\n### Key constraints (from user)\n- **Discovery is NOT skipped** — /dui-discover runs as an early phase inside this skill. The EUI baseline is crucial.\n- **Phased execution with pauses** — the skill runs in numbered phases, pausing after each to report what was done and wait for user to say "continue", "stop", or "elaborate on X"\n- **User stays in control** — no phase auto-advances. User sees results before committing to next phase.\n\n### Phases (each pauses for user approval)\n\n**Phase 0: Init + Discover**\n- Run /dui-init (creates YAML if missing)\n- Run /dui-discover (captures EUI baseline — layout profile, fields, load elements, screenshots)\n- Prompt user for load values and special notes\n- PAUSE: report page structure, layout profile, widget inventory\n\n**Phase 1: Read & Analyze EUI source**\n- Read EUI pug + EUI JS\n- Identify every widget (qbe, combobox, datebox, datagrid, tree, menu, tabs)\n- Map toolbar relationships (which datagrid owns which toolbar via toolbar:\'#tbar\')\n- Map formatters, event handlers, custom functions\n- Cross-reference with migration map for known translations\n- PAUSE: report widget inventory, toolbar relationships, identified patterns\n\n**Phase 2: Generate DUI pug**\n- Read mixin signatures from html/dui/mixins/*.pug\n- Read reference page (sa_parts.pug) for correct patterns\n- Convert each EUI element to correct DUI mixin call with reasoning\n- Handle toolbar context (inline fitem, embedded in datagrid)\n- Handle layout (regions → vsplit/hsplit with panel wrappers)\n- Preserve widget types (qbe stays qbe, combobox stays combobox)\n- PAUSE: show the generated pug, report conversion decisions\n\n**Phase 3: Generate DUI JS + JSON configs**\n- Translate page JS: dwap → $.page, add hooks, wire events\n- Extract datagrid column configs to JSON files\n- Preserve formatters, custom functions\n- Remove deprecated code (butEn, linkbutton, editButs)\n- PAUSE: show the generated JS, report what was translated/removed\n\n**Phase 4: Browser verification**\n- Restart server, open DUI page\n- Load data using baseline values\n- Screenshot and compare with EUI baseline screenshot\n- Check console errors\n- PAUSE: show screenshot, report any visible issues\n\n**Phase 5: Commit**\n- Write migrator YAML with status\n- Commit all generated files\n- Report summary\n\n### Inputs\n1. EUI pug + JS (source of truth)\n2. Migration map (pattern translations)\n3. Mixin signatures (correct call syntax)\n4. Reference page sa_parts (known-good example)\n5. EUI baseline from /dui-discover (layout, fields, screenshots)\n\n### Outputs\n1. DUI pug — correct mixin usage from the start\n2. DUI JS — translated with $.page patterns\n3. Datagrid JSON configs\n4. Updated migrator YAML\n\n### Pipeline impact\n- /dui-audit becomes optional sanity check\n- /dui-fix handles only runtime edge cases\n- /dui-fix-dgedit may be absorbed into Phase 2\n- Pipeline shrinks from 7 steps to: discover → migrate → verify → layout'}
2026-03-01 12:58:27,659 416824 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': 'Research complete. Read:\n- EUI part_plan pug+JS (the source of truth)\n- Current broken DUI part_plan pug+JS (shows script failures)\n- sa_parts.pug (reference page — correct DUI patterns)\n- migration-map.yaml (all EUI→DUI translations)\n- layout-map.yaml (layout patterns)\n- split-panel.md (layout mixin docs)\n- input.pug, datagrid.pug (mixin signatures)\n- Existing dui-migrate SKILL.md (just wraps dumb script)\n- dui-discover, dui-init, dui-audit, dui-verify, dui-layout skills\n\nKey design decisions for the new skill:\n1. Phase 0 runs /dui-init then /dui-discover (not skippable)\n2. Each phase pauses for user approval\n3. Phase 1 analyzes EUI source and reports widget inventory\n4. Phase 2 generates DUI pug with reasoning per element\n5. Phase 3 generates DUI JS + JSON configs\n6. Phase 4 browser verification\n7. Phase 5 commit'}
