2026-03-01 17:46:39,555 448637 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': "## Phase 2: EUI → DUI Component Map for sa_jobplan\n\n| EUI Component | DUI Equivalent | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `$('#el').datagrid(...)` | `$.dui.datagrid` — same jQuery call pattern | datagrid-plugin |\n| `$('#el').combobox(...)` | `$.dui.combobox` — same jQuery call pattern | combobox-plugin |\n| `$('#el').linkbutton(...)` | `$.dui.linkbutton` — same jQuery call pattern | linkbutton-plugin |\n| `$('#el').window(...)` | `$.dui.window` — `$('#el').window(...)` / `$('#el').modal(...)` | modal-plugin, window is alias |\n| `$('#el').tooltip({onShow})` | **NO EQUIVALENT** | DUI tooltip is CSS `data-tip` only, no dynamic onShow |\n| `$('#el').menu('show',{left,top})` | **NO EQUIVALENT** | No context menu plugin |\n| `$('#el').progressbar({value})` | **NO EQUIVALENT** | No progressbar plugin |\n| `$('#el').draggable(...)` | jQuery UI `$.ui.draggable` | Loaded by DUI layout |\n| `$('#el').droppable(...)` | jQuery UI `$.ui.droppable` | Loaded by DUI layout |\n| `dwap.page.*` | `$.page.fn.*` | Page-specific functions |\n| `dwap.page.planplus` | `$.dui.page.planplus` | Page data property |\n| `dwap.page.stats` | `$.dui.page.stats` | Page data property |\n| `dwap.bhave` | `$.dui.bhave` | Global behaviour |\n| `ajaxget(url, params, cb)` | `ajaxget(url, params, cb)` | Shimmed, same signature |\n| `linkwin(link)` | `linkwin(link)` | Shimmed |\n| `myTime(date)` | `myTime(date)` | Shimmed via misc-plugin |\n| `butEn(...)` | **DEPRECATED** — toolbar-plugin manages | Remove |\n\n### 3 genuinely missing APIs for this page:\n1. Context menu (`$.dui.menu` show at position) — #opnmenu right-click\n2. Dynamic tooltip (onShow with content builder) — #stats Planner Stats\n3. Progressbar — #appprog AutoPlan progress"}
