tton({}) init call\n\n### JS AST TRANSFORMS (5)\nCOVERED(3): loadData→hook, dwap.page.fn→$.page.fn, dwap.page refs\nPARTIAL(1): $.page.ready() wrapper — SKILL.md mentions but no map entry\n\n### JS SELECTORS (2) — all COVERED\n\n### INDEX.JS POST-STEPS (10)\nMISSING(2): extends ../content injection, fragment include rename with _ prefix\nPARTIAL(1): datagrid JSON extraction (conceptually covered in SKILL.md)\nN/A(7): process/bookkeeping steps replaced by YAML\n\n## Implementation Steps\n1. Add 13 pug_patterns to migration-map.yaml (easyui prefix strip, tooltip title, column layouts, center→text-center, hide→hidden, jqm classes, linkbutton in styles, inline html form, script src paths, raw-fieldset, raw-button, raw-label, surface overrides broad)\n2. Add 6 namespace entries (dwap.menu, dwap.udata, dwap.pdata, dwap.ronly, dwap.runmode, dwap.doc)\n3. Add 4 JS patterns (eui_datetime, input_fkey_selector, linkbutton_init, page_ready_wrapper)\n4. Update SKILL.md Phase 2 with: extends injection, fragment include rename, fragment detection\n5. Resume sa_jobplan migration Phase 2+\n\n## Files\n- docs/dui/migration-map.yaml — add ~22 entries\n- .claude/skills/dui-migrate/SKILL.md — add structural steps to Phase 2'}
