2026-03-01 19:29:27,423 472725 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## Plan\n\n### Phase 1: Complete the map\n1. Add 30 missing/partial items from audit to migration-map.yaml (pug patterns, namespace entries, JS patterns — all in one pass)\n2. Scan the completed map for duplicate or conflicting rules and resolve them\n\n### Phase 2: Build the learning loop\n3. Create reference register YAML (docs/dui/reference-files.yaml) — list of known-good converted pages with metadata\n4. Create /dui-learn skill — runs /dui-state on each reference page to populate/refresh register metadata, diffs EUI↔DUI pairs against migration-map.yaml, flags gaps/errors/conflicts, proposes updates\n5. Run /dui-learn — first execution validates the now-complete map against 8 reference files, apply improvements\n\n### Phase 3: Continue migration\n6. Update SKILL.md Phase 2 with structural steps (extends injection, fragment rename)\n7. Resume sa_jobplan migration — success adds it to the register for future /dui-learn runs\n\n## Audit Data (from previous session)\n23 MISSING + 7 PARTIAL items. See previous plan note for full breakdown by category.\n\n## Files\n- docs/dui/migration-map.yaml — add ~22 entries, scan for conflicts\n- docs/dui/reference-files.yaml — NEW, register of known-good pages\n- .claude/skills/dui-learn/SKILL.md — NEW, learning skill\n- .claude/skills/dui-migrate/SKILL.md — add structural steps to Phase 2'}
