2026-03-01 20:00:31,872 472725 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Create $.dui.fmt formatter namespace and migrate eui.* formatters', 'description': 'Create a DUI formatter namespace ($.dui.fmt) to replace the legacy eui.* global object. Add shim so eui.* proxies to $.dui.fmt.* during transition. Update migration-map.yaml entries.'}
2026-03-01 20:00:45,929 472725 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 6, 'text': "## Source: public/js/eui.extend.js (line 10)\n\n`var eui = {}` is a global object loaded on every page. NOT broken at runtime — all `eui.*` references work. Migration is modernization, not bug fix.\n\n## Functions to migrate\n\n| eui.* | $.dui.fmt.* | Implementation |\n|-------|-------------|----------------|\n| eui.date | $.dui.fmt.date | `val.match(/^[0-9\\|-]*/)[0]` |\n| eui.currency | $.dui.fmt.currency | `'$' + $.dui.fmt.number(val, 2)` |\n| eui.integer | $.dui.fmt.integer | `$.dui.fmt.number(val)` |\n| eui.number | $.dui.fmt.number | `parseFloat(val).toFixed(dec)` |\n| eui.table | $.dui.fmt.table | Builds HTML table from columns + rows |\n| eui.ref2text | $.dui.fmt.ref2text | `val.replace(/\\^/g, '.')` |\n\n## Other eui.* functions (not formatters — separate concern)\n- eui.aliases — form alias helper\n- eui.colsort — datagrid column sorter\n- eui.droplist — drag-and-drop list\n- eui.translate — language translation\n- eui.formatValue — textbox format helper\n- eui.isloading — form loading check\n- eui.navdelay, eui.ajax_method — config values\n\nThese non-formatter functions need a separate home (utils-plugin or dedicated plugins).\n\n## Implementation plan\n1. Create $.dui.fmt in a DUI plugin (formatter-plugin.js or add to dui-namespace.js)\n2. Copy formatter functions to $.dui.fmt.*\n3. Add shim: make `window.eui` proxy to $.dui.fmt for backward compat\n4. Update migration-map.yaml: eui_date, eui_currency, eui_integer entries with $.dui.fmt.* as dui target\n5. Add missing map entries: eui_currency, eui_integer, eui_table, eui_number\n\n## Pages affected (from validation)\n- inv/purchase_manager: eui.currency (3), eui.date (1), eui.table (1)\n- sales/quote_man: eui.currency in JSON (2), eui.date in JSON (1)\n- inv/sa_parts: eui.date (7)\n- sales/contact_man: eui.date (2)"}
